            <p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial">
            <font size="2" color="#570E0A">The climate of the region is mild 
            though the mountains provide a certain degree of aridity. The 
            temperature in Summer ranges from 18º C to 33º C and days are hot 
            and nights are fresh. In Winter, the minimum temperature is 3º C and 
            the maximum registered temperature is 16º C</font></span></p>
