            <p><font color="#570E0A">
            <span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial"><font size="2">
            Argentina´s current population is more than 36 million inhabitants. 
            The total population of Mendoza Province is around 1,700,000, of 
            which approximately 800,000 reside in the city area. Population 
            density calculated on a national basis is 13 inhabitants per square 
