            <font size="2">S</font></span><font color="#570E0A" size="2"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial">armiento 
            street running through its center. Other major streets, running 
            perpendicular to Sarmiento, are 9 de Julio St., San Martín Avenue, 
            and running parallel to Sarmiento are avenues Colón, Arístides 
            Villanueva and Las Heras. Many small parks, known as &quot;plazas&quot; are 
            spread within the city</span></font></p>
